# Requirements
'''
### [GEANT4v10.6.3](https://github.com/Geant4/geant4/releases/tag/v10.6.3)

### [HDF5](https://www.hdfgroup.org/solutions/hdf5/)

or
sudo apt-get install libhdf5-serial-dev(UBUNTU)

### CMake
sudo apt-get install cmake (UBUNTU)

'''
# Instalation for ubuntu.
'''
git clone -b CRAB https://github.com/ilkerparmaksiz/nexus
cd nexus
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
if there is no error
make -j4
sudo make install
'''

# Running
### Interactive mode
./build/source/nexus -i macros/CRAB/CRAB_CS137_init.mac

### batch mode
./build/source/nexus -n 1 macros/CRAB/CRAB_CS137_init.mac
